{"fields":{"body":[{"value":"In 1965 Helen Schucman and William Thetford were drawn together by the compulsion of Helen’s inner voice that said, “This is a Course in Miracles, please take notes.” Over the next several years, the two worked together to produce a volume of text that would change the lives of many people all over the world.\n\nThe Foundation for Inner Peace published the text, and thus ACIM program - also known simply as “the Course” - was born. Today, prominent luminaries including Marianne Williamson, Judith Skutch Whitson and Dr. Gerald Jampolski tell of their experiences with the Course. In essence, this self-study program is a form of psychotherapy with a Christian context that has nothing to do with the past 2,000 years of biblical teachings. These teachings come to life through spoken narration and dramatizations of allegories in the book. Watch with an open mind, and learn how A Course in Miracles has helped many people find their spiritual paths.\n","format":1}],"teaser":[{"value":"In 1965 Helen Schucman and William Thetford were drawn together by the compulsion of Helen’s inner voice that said, “This is a Course in Miracles, please take notes”. Spoken narration and dramatizations of allegories bring the teachings to life in this documentary.","format":1}],"series_nid":[{"nid":null}],"season":[{"value":null}],"episode":[{"value":null}],"instructor":[{"value":null}],"director":[{"value":"Penny Price"}],"producer":[{"value":"Penny Price"}],"writer":[{"value":"Penny Price"}],"cast":[{"value":"Marianne Williamson, Dr. Gerald Jampolski, Kenneth Wapnick, Judith Skutch Whitson, Gary Renard"}],"copyright":[{"value":"2006"}],"studio":[{"value":"Penny Price Media"}],"video_lang":[{"value":"English"}]},"drupal_cache":"not-drupal","nid":31472,"type":"product_video","language":"en","primaryLanguage":"en","cta":{"label":null,"path":null,"deeplinkPath":null},"title":"A Course in Miracles","promote":0,"status":1,"comment_count":72,"created":1372679960,"refere